info.description: Header works best zoomed in at 110%. All the black Catiel fans (all casty fans in general tbh) want that kiss right? Well, just as Chino won't let us be black in game, she won't give us a kiss either. But never fear Dues-ex to the rescue!!! I have no idea who edited Castiel as Dake, but I did the skin color edit myself. BONUS: your morale icon is now a black girl with a fro!
